<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>About · Seasonal Notes</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #f7f4ee;
      --ink: #2f2720;
      --note-bg: #fffdf6;
      --note-border: #e0d4b8;
      --link-bg: #fff3b8;
      --link-border: #e0c46a;
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 2.5rem 1.5rem 3rem;
      font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--ink);
      line-height: 1.6;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .page {
      max-width: 720px;
      width: 100%;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin: 0 0 1rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    }

    .about-note {
      background: var(--note-bg);
      border: 1px solid var(--note-border);
      border-radius: 0.7rem;
      padding: 1.2rem 1.1rem 1.1rem;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
      transform: rotate(-1.2deg);
      max-width: 34rem;
    }

    .about-note p {
      margin: 0 0 0.7rem;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .about-note p:last-child {
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .back-link-wrapper {
      margin-top: 1.8rem;
    }

    .back-link {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 0.4rem 0.7rem;
      background: var(--link-bg);
      border: 1px solid var(--link-border);
      border-radius: 0.35rem;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: var(--ink);
      box-shadow: 0 2px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
      transform: rotate(-1deg);
      transition: transform 0.12s ease, box-shadow 0.12s ease;
    }

    .back-link:hover {
      transform: rotate(0deg) translateY(-1px);
      box-shadow: 0 3px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.16);
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      body {
        padding: 1.8rem 1.1rem 2.4rem;
      }
      h1 {
        font-size: 1.8rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="page">
    <header>
      <h1>About this artefact</h1>
    </header>

    <main>
      <section class="about-note">
        <p>
          Seasonal Notes is a single page arranged like a desk scattered with slips of paper:
          fragments grouped by season rather than by topic or importance.
        </p>
        <p>
          Each block is a small weather system—colour, mood, and margin doodles shifting around it.
          The notes are intentionally short and narrow, closer to the size of something you’d
          scribble in the margin than something you’d publish in a column.
        </p>
        <p>
          The hand-drawn SVG marks are not photographs of paint, but they borrow its logic:
          soft edges, imperfect outlines, and a sense that they could have been added after
          the words, in a quiet moment.
        </p>
      </section>

      <div class="back-link-wrapper">
        <a href="/" class="back-link">Back to Seasonal Notes</a>
      </div>
    </main>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
